snippet.title: LEO - Badass Lyric | Thalapathy Vijay | Lokesh Kanagaraj | Anirudh Ravichander
snippet.description:
The Baddest Badass is here! Check out this full-blooded rager featuring the OG Badass #ThalapathyVijay, in the fiery voice of #AnirudhRavichander that is about scorch all the charts and workout playlists for the foreseeable future! Stream this fire song as many times as you can, because we just cannot seem to get enough! 


Song Title : Badass
Album / Movie : Leo
Composed by Anirudh Ravichander
Lyrics - Vishnu Edavan
Vocals - Anirudh Ravichander

Composed, Arranged & Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander 
Additional Vocals by Prudhvi Chandra
Electric & Bass Guitar by Keba Jeremiah
Trumpet by Rakesh
EL Fe Choir by Roe Vincent 
Keyboard, Synth & Rhythm Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander
Rhythm Produced by Shashank Vijay
Additional Keyboard Programmed Arish & Pradeep PJ
Music Advisor - Ananthakrrishnan
Creative Consultant - Sajith Satya

Recorded at Albuquerque Records, Chennai. 
Engineered by Srinivasan M, Shivakiran S, Rajesh Kannan
Trumpet Recorded by Vibe_N Studios, Chennai Engineered by Lokesh Vijayakumar
Mixed by Vinay Sridhar & Srinivasan M at Albuquerque Records, Chennai
Mastered by Luca Pretolesi at Studio DMI, Las Vegas, Assisted by
Music Coordinator - Velavan B
 
Starring - Thalapathy Vijay, Sanjay Dutt, Trisha, Priya Anand, Arjun, Mansoor Ali Khan
Written & Directed by Lokesh Kanagaraj
Music : Anirudh Ravichander
Producer : Lalit Kumar
Co Producer : Jagadish Palanisamy
Banner : Seven Screen Studio
Director of Photography : Manoj Paramahamsa
Action : Anbariv 
Editor : Philomin Raj

Choreography : Dinesh

snippet.description:

Tiger Ka Message Video:
Background Music: Tanuj Tiku
Original Tiger Theme Composition: Julius Packiam

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War," was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. The recent release Pathaan (2023) starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham is the fourth instalment in the spy universe franchise.

All the films of the Spy Universe are blockbusters with Pathaan being the all-time highest grossing Hindi film ever. The YRF Spy Universe is now one of the biggest IP’s in the history of Indian cinema. The next film from this franchise is Tiger 3 releasing this Diwali!

YRF Spy Universe films boast of incredible visual spectacles with high-octane action sequences, thrilling plot-lines, power-packed characters and musical chartbusters.

In this candid interview, they take you on a journey through the pages of their romance, revealing the moments that brought them together and the deep bond that unites them.
 As they share their unknown love story, you'll witness the genuine chemistry and affection that makes them not just a beloved on-screen pair but a cherished couple in real life. From the early days of their relationship to the memorable proposal, this interview is a celebration of love in the world of cinema.

snippet.title: Asian Games: Nepal's Dipendra Airee Smashes 50 Off 9 Balls, Breaks Yuvraj Singh’s Record | The Quint
snippet.description:
Dipendra Singh Airee of Nepal on Wednesday achieved the fastest fifty, taking only nine balls to break Yuvraj Singh's 16-year-old record set during the 2007 T20 World Cup match against England.

In the group match of the ongoing Asian Games, Dipendra scored an unbeaten 52 off just 10 balls against Mongolia here at the Pingfeng Cricket Field. His record knock was studded with eight sixes.

Watch the LIVE coverage of 19th Asian Games Hangzhou 2022 on Sony Sports Ten 1, Sony Sports Ten 2, Sony Sports Ten 3, Sony Sports Ten 4, Sony Sports Ten 5 channels from 23rd September to 8th October 2023.

snippet.title: Mission Raniganj: The Great Bharat Rescue | Official Trailer | Akshay Kumar | In Cinemas 6th October
snippet.description:
Get ready to witness one of the largest coal mine rescue missions, INSPIRED BY A REAL HERO, Jaswant Singh Gill! ✨

#MissionRaniganj IN CINEMAS on 6th October.

Book your tickets on BookMyShow and get ₹200 off* - https://in.bookmyshow.com/movie-voucher/BSTR/2001373 

MISSION RANIGANJ - The Great Bharat Rescue is inspired by a real-life hero, Late Jaswant Singh Gill, an engineer who led a challenging rescue mission to save trapped miners from a flooded coal mine. This edge-of-the-seat thriller highlights Gill's courage and relentless efforts, showcasing his resilience to overcome adversities. A race against time rescue mission starring Akshay Kumar and Parineeti Chopra in the lead with a talented ensemble cast - Kumund Mishra, Rajesh Sharma, Pavan Malhotra, Ravi Kishan, Dibyendu Bhattacharya and Varun Badola to name a few.

Vashu Bhagnani & Pooja Entertainment Presents

snippet.title: 75 HARD DAY CHALLENGE - @Ankitbaiyanpuria | Desi Diet & Workout | Bharti TV | LOL PODCAST EP - 3
snippet.description:
राम राम भाई सरियाने, जैसे ही सुनते हैं, तो याद आता है अंकित और अंकित का '75 हार्ड चैलेंज'. सोनीपत के एक छोटे से गांव के एक लड़के ने पूरे भारत में '75 हार्ड' को इस क़दर प्रसिद्ध कर दिया है कि अब हजारों नहीं, लाखों लोग इस चैलेंज को कर रहे हैं, और इसी बहाने हमारा देश स्वस्थ हो रहा है। आज हमने अंकित के साथ उसके गांव, दोस्तों और परिवार के साथ, साथ ही एक देसी डाइट और देसी वर्कआउट के महत्व पर भी चर्चा की... आशा करते हैं कि आपको यह एपिसोड पसंद आए।

"Ram Ram, my friends, as soon as you hear that greeting, it brings to mind Ankit and his '75 Hard Day Challenge.' A young man from a small village in Sonipat has made '75 Hard Day Challenge' so famous across India that now not just thousands, but millions of people are taking up this challenge, and as a result, our country is becoming healthier. Today, we have Ankit with us to discuss the importance of his village, friends, and family, as well as the significance of a desi diet and desi workout. We hope you enjoy this episode."

Time Stamp 

(00:00) - Precap
(00:38) - Intro
(00:49) - Episode start
(02:00) - Fitness mai kaise aaye ?
(04:42) - Thought behind 75 hard 
(06:32) - Family 
(06:45) - How do you manage your expenses? 
(07:54) - Reaction of village people
(09:02) - Badam Ragda 
(11:10) - Sapate 
(13:32) - Veg vs non - veg food & weight loss
(15:30) - 5 exercises for weight loose

localized.title: 75 HARD DAY CHALLENGE - @Ankitbaiyanpuria | Desi Diet & Workout | Bharti TV | LOL PODCAST EP - 3
localized.description:
राम राम भाई सरियाने, जैसे ही सुनते हैं, तो याद आता है अंकित और अंकित का '75 हार्ड चैलेंज'. सोनीपत के एक छोटे से गांव के एक लड़के ने पूरे भारत में '75 हार्ड' को इस क़दर प्रसिद्ध कर दिया है कि अब हजारों नहीं, लाखों लोग इस चैलेंज को कर रहे हैं, और इसी बहाने हमारा देश स्वस्थ हो रहा है। आज हमने अंकित के साथ उसके गांव, दोस्तों और परिवार के साथ, साथ ही एक देसी डाइट और देसी वर्कआउट के महत्व पर भी चर्चा की... आशा करते हैं कि आपको यह एपिसोड पसंद आए।

"Ram Ram, my friends, as soon as you hear that greeting, it brings to mind Ankit and his '75 Hard Day Challenge.' A young man from a small village in Sonipat has made '75 Hard Day Challenge' so famous across India that now not just thousands, but millions of people are taking up this challenge, and as a result, our country is becoming healthier. Today, we have Ankit with us to discuss the importance of his village, friends, and family, as well as the significance of a desi diet and desi workout. We hope you enjoy this episode."

snippet.title: Sarkaare | Official Music Video | New Life | KING
snippet.description:
A modern-day crooner at his effervescent best, ‘Sarkaare’ is a smoothly bumping glide and KING’s unbeatable pop sensibilities coming together for a pure pop cut while drawing his influences from vintage melodies of the early 2000s Bollywood which continue to consistently tug at Indian and diaspora listeners’ heart strings over decades.

STREAM NOW : http://out-now.lnk.to/Sarkaare

Song Name : Sarkaare
Artist: KING
Lyrics : KING, Alan Sampson, Sophia Brennan
Music Producer : Alan Sampson
Composed by : KING, Alan Sampson, Sophia Brennan
Recording Engineer : Samir Dharap at Studio 504
Female Vocals : Priyanshi Srivastava
Vocal Production : Akarsh Shetty, Hanish Taneja, Priyanshi Srivastava
Mixed by : Hanish Taneja at Studio Alika
Mastered by : Luca Pretolesi at Studio DMI (Assisted by Alistair Pintus)
Artwork : Orisis

Directed and Edited by : Arsh Grewal

Production Team : Ashish Garg, Kartik Gola

Make up : Archana Gurung

Follow King: 
Spotify : https://lnk.to/KingSpotify 
Apple : https://out-now.lnk.to/KingApple 
YouTube :  https://lnk.to/KingYouTube 
Instagram : https://lnk.to/KingInstagram 
Facebook : https://lnk.to/KingFacebook 
Twitter : https://lnk.to/KingTwitter 
Snapchat : https://lnk.to/KingSnapchat 
WHATSAPP : https://lnk.to/Whatsapp_
  
Follow Warner Music India :   
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/warnermusicindia
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/WarnerMusicInd  
Twitter : https://twitter.com/warnermusicin

Lyrics : 
Dil ko dukha ke thoda hum bhi dekhenge
Yaadon mein basa ke thoda hum bhi dekhenge
Shayad hum juda hue toh phir na milein

Ho,
Na ja sarkaare,
Dekh toh yahan re,
Pyaar ke hain maare,
Jaise tute taare,
Hai bechare, 
Kayi saare,
Kayi saare.

Ho, main kya karti ek bahana chun liya.
Ho, tere chehre ka sirhaana bunn liya.

Tuta jo taara, 
Zameen pe hara, 
Khwab humara, 
Falling from the sky,
Samjhe ishara, 
Kehna kya chahra,
Saansein bachi na,
Love me back to life.

Love me back to life

Na dekha tune haal yeh mera,
Muqaddar bhi sath na mera,
Begaano si mai nachdi phiru,
Teri jogan banke saajna.

Is hi tarah din katega mera,
Raatein hongi meri tanha,
Tu sunega nahi,
Mai bhi bolungi na, 
Tujhse pyaar kiya.

Ho, jo tu hi nahi hai,
Kya paas hamare,
Vahi dil dooba re,
Jaha na kinara, 
Na sahara, 
Na tumhara, 
Na humara.

Ho, mai kya karti ek bahana chun liya.
Ho, tere chehre ka sirhaana bunn liya.

Toota jo taara, 
Zameen pe haara,
Khwaab humara,
Falling from the sky,
Samjhe ishara,
Kehna kya chahra, 
Saansein bachi na,
Love me back to life.

#ElvishYadav #DGIMMORTALS #Bawli
_______________________________________________________________________________

Artists: DG IMMORTALS, Elvish Yadav
Music: Yawar

Director: Deepesh Goyal
DOP: Vikcee
Choreographer: Amit Syal, Ankit Thapa
Chief AD: Parteek Bangia
Editor/DI: Bharat Mittal, Deepesh Goyal
Line Production: Kulbir Bhatia
Publicity Design: Sumit Bamal
Background Score: Apsy Singh

Lyrics:

Tu soche Gaadi me ghumaunga
No chance
Terepe paisa udaunga
Not anymore
Tere nakhre uthaoge
Never girl 
Tu leri halke me soche
Tere jaal me aaaunga

Chhori baavli ho ri h k ?
Kaise karke manegi ?
chhori baavli ho ri h k ?
Kaise karke manegi 

Phela hi bata di thi 
Mane tere tey 
Babu Shona baby nhi
Hoga mere tey
Karegi pyar toh laga dunga
Paiso Mai aag 
Paiso de pyar karegi toh
Karlunga cut off Mai

Chori teri jaise bohot khilayi hai 
Bohot ghumayi hai 
Daru pila k club Mai 
Bohot nachayi 
Ek raat wali rasam mane 
Bohot nibayi 
Dikhaye chand tare 
Chakhayi dodh malai 

Bitayi raat tere sath toh ab
Din ka kya kaam 
Tane jana hai toh ja 
Tere dil ka kya kaam 
Mane yaad nahi ave tu 
ayi kis shyam 
Kya waqt kya thi jagha
Aur kya tha tera naam

Chori bawli ho ri hai k ?
Rey Maka bawli ho ri hai k ?

Haryane ka hai chora
Pure desh mai Tora
Systumm hang karta chale
RAO Sahab ka yo chora 

Chora kache kate khoob 
Rakhe loaded bandook 
Khud chore ki security Ka dhyan rakha bhola 

Jabi kise tey na dare chora 

Chori meri lat lagi tane toh 
Roz ana padega 
Roz shyam jaam gel gram lana padega 
Saaf baat chori mane nakhre na pasand 
Tane rehna hai toh systumm k niche rehna padega 

Yo Rao sahab tere hath mai na avega

Chhori baavli ho ri h k ?
Kaise karke manegi ?
Chhori baavli ho ri h k ?
Kaise karke manegi

--------------------------------------------------------
Everyone enjoys their tea at the society's compound when Taarak spills his green tea. Popatlal and other members of the Purush Mandali ask him to have their masala tea. Anjali stops everyone and exposes Taarak's and Popat's idea of fooling her as she plans to make another green tea for Taarak. The Purush Mandali tries to persuade Anjali to allow Taarak to have masala chai with them. The next morning, everyone is ecstatic to see the decorations at the Ganpati pandal, Bhide congratulates Tapu Sena for their efforts and gives them a full score. Watch the episode.

Episode 3887: Secret Decoration
--------------------------------------------------------
After the previous speakers stopped working, Tapu Sena purchased pricey speakers. Tapu Sena infuriates Bhide by spending a lot of money on new speakers. Bhide is informed by Tapu Sena that Jetha has financed this and not the community as a whole. Jetha is questioned about his actions by Bhide over the phone. The speakers are for the Ganapati festival, not as a favor, Jetha informs Bhide. Finally, Bhide concurs with Jetha and instructs Tapu Sena to retain them. Everyone in Gokuldham is eager to learn later about the theme that Tapu Sena has chosen for Ganesh Chaturthi this year.

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2 | Flowers | EP# 347
snippet.description:
ഹൈമവതിയ്ക്ക് കാര്യമായി എന്തോ സംഭവിച്ചിട്ടുണ്ട്. എന്ത് ചെയ്യണമെന്നറിയാതെ രാം കുമാർ. ഹൈമവതിയോട് സംസാരിച്ച് കാര്യം മനസിലാക്കാൻ ശ്രമിച്ച് നീലു. പക്ഷെ സംഭവം കയ്യിൽ നിൽക്കുമെന്ന് തോന്നുന്നില്ല. എന്തു സംഭവിക്കുമെന്ന് കാത്തിരുന്ന് കാണാം!!

"Something serious has happened to Haimavathi. Ram Kumar does not know what to do. Neelu tries to understand what her problem is. But the incident does not seem to be under control. Let's wait and see what happens in 'Uppum Mulakum'!!"

needs (SEN). We firmly believe that every child deserves the best possible start in life, and our dedicated team is committed to helping each child

become school-ready, i.e., prepared to learn together with peers in

snippet.title: How much 'Titanium' does iPhone 15 Pro *actually* have? -  NO SECRETS HERE!
snippet.description:
Today we completely dismantle a new iPhone 15 Pro Max to see how much titanium Apple has overlayed onto their aluminum frame. Anker Nano USB-C Fast Charging Lineup for iPhone 15 on Amazon: https://ankerfast.club/HNUBgh and on Anker.com: https://shop.anker.com/21iTX8 According to lab tests, the 5,000mAh Anker Nano Power Bank can charge an iPhone 15 to 79%. Power loss from internal components may prevent a full charge.

Titanium is a really expensive material. Titanium is also EXTREMELY difficult to work with. But its really cool to see how Apple has assembled their new iPhone 15 Pro Max from the inside. We also take apart Apple's Tetra-Prism camera to see how the 5x Telephoto lens functions. 

Get my Teardown Skin for your phone HERE: https://www.dbrand.com/teardown
Get my JerryRig Razor knife HERE: https://www.jerryrigknife.com/

Follow me for updates! 
Instagram: http://instagram.com/zacksjerryrig 
Facebook: http://on.fb.me/1U4bQqv 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ZacksJerryRig 

LARGE tool kit: http://amzn.to/2DURcr7 
Travel Tool Kit: https://amzn.to/30LKXOY 
Mega Tool Kit: https://amzn.to/2OwequL 
Plastic Pry tools: http://amzn.to/1Tu57pI 
Metal phone opening tool: http://amzn.to/1WdOFv0 
The camera I used to film this video: http://amzn.to/2p7GtkX (GH6 https://amzn.to/3LyfW8d) 
The Lens I used for this video: http://amzn.to/1QOXDw2 
Wide angle lens: http://amzn.to/2qiYM4u 
And this Metabones adapter: http://amzn.to/2iZ67Ty 
This is the drone I use: https://amzn.to/3JEuTXs

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3886 | 26 Sep 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3886: Kharab Speaker
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha is taken aback when he sees Bagha, and Nattu Kaka has posted a special notice about the "Mega Sale" at the store. Bagha explains to Jetha why such a declaration was made. He and Nattu Kaka have devised a strategy for the store's stock removal. Finally, Jetha expresses relief and commends them on their profitable concept. Meanwhile, Bhide presents Madhvi with a beautiful saree for Ganesh Chaturthi. Sonu becomes moved after witnessing Bhide and Madhvi's adorable moment. Later, when Tapu arrives to meet Sonu, Bhide is dissatisfied.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3886, 26 Sep 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:

Jetha comes and meets Sodhi. They both notice Bhide writing a long 'Suvichar' so they decide to ask him about it. Jetha learns that all of them have to prepare a speech on the occasion of Republic Day. He gets nervous and shares the news with Iyer and Babita. Later, Jetha goes back home to inform Bapuji and Daya about the same.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 306
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #comedy2023 #jethalal 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Revisit The Journey: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSkLfD49YxG8YsjmWdKNU0r

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Last Episode 42 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 25th September 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Imran Abbas as Shani
Neelam Muneer as Shanzay
Nimra Khan as Sajeela
Mahmood Aslam as Kamran
Ismat Zaidi as Kulsoom
Maira Khan as Nadiya
Zainab Qayoom as Samiya
Saqib Sameer as Khawar
Aadi Khan as Jugnu

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

snippet.title: Kalank Episode 34 - [Eng Sub]  Hira Mani - Junaid Khan - Nazish Jahangir - Sami Khan - 27th Sep 2023
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kalank Episode 34 - [Eng Sub]  Hira Mani - Junaid Khan - Nazish Jahangir - Sami Khan - 27th Sep 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Kalank" follows Sara, a determined MBA graduate seeking a job while living with her parents. Her aunt perceives Sara as a threat to her daughter's wedding prospects, adding tension to their household. Meanwhile, Sara and her cousin Wahaj develop feelings for each other, leading to potential marriage plans.
However, Sara's faces a set of unfortunate events when she joins a new office and encounters Sarfaraz, a manager with malicious intent. He defames and disrespects her, triggering a series of troubles and crises in her professional and personal life.
As false accusations tarnish her reputation, Sara faces an uphill battle to prove her innocence. The drama intensifies as doubts and skepticism surround her. Will she be able to restore her credibility and regain her standing in society? Amidst the chaos, the future of Sara and Wahaj's relationship hangs in the balance. Will their love survive the challenges posed by external forces and family pressure?

Written by: Edison Idrees Masih
Directed by: Mohsin Mirza
Produced by: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast:

Saba Hameed - Shahana

🌟 Embark on an EPIC adventure with me and my local pals as we journey deep into the heart of the Shappiere mining site! 🌍

🔦 Prepare to be AMAZED as we venture into the mysterious underground world of mining, where the treasures of the Earth are hidden away, waiting to be discovered! 💎

🌋 But hold on tight, because this journey takes an UNEXPECTED turn! 😱 Watch as I fearlessly explore the intricate tunnels and chambers, sharing every moment of this thrilling expedition with you.

🚧 Just when we thought we'd seen it all, we encounter a treacherous pit that tests our courage and survival skills. 😮 Will I make it out alive? You'll have to WATCH to find out!
🎤 And oh, did I mention that things get even MORE intense? Yes, that's right! I lost my microphone during this incredible escapade, so you'll experience all the heart-pounding action with the raw and unfiltered sounds of the mining site!
🔥 This is a YouTube experience like no other, filled with adventure, adrenaline, and unexpected twists! Don't miss out – hit that SUBSCRIBE button, give this video a THUMBS UP, and join me on this unforgettable journey into the depths of Shappiere mining site!
🔔 Make sure to turn on your NOTIFICATIONS so you're the first to know when the next thrilling episode drops! Get ready to be on the edge of your seat as we explore the unknown together!

#MiningAdventure #Exploration #UnexpectedTwist #LostMic #undergroundexploration

நான் புவனி தரன், பேக் பேக்கர், ஹிட்சிகர், வோல்கர் & ட்ரெக்கர், உலகம் முழுவதும் பயணம் செய்து எனது அனுபவங்களை அனைவருடனும் பகிர்ந்து கொள்கிறேன்.

புதிய இடங்களைப் பார்ப்பது, வெவ்வேறு கலாச்சாரத்தை அனுபவிப்பது, மக்களைப் பற்றி அறிந்து கொள்வது, இந்த அழகான உலகத்தை தமிழ் ட்ரெக்கர் வழியாக உங்களுக்குக் காட்ட முயற்சிப்பேன்.

I'm Bhuvani Dharan, Solo travel enthusiast, Backpacker, hitchhiker, vlogger & trekker who travels the world and shares my experiences with everyone.

My videos consist of my spontaneous everyday life as each day is a new adventure.

Love to see new places, experience different culture, learn about people, taste different food and more. I will try to show you this beautiful world via Tamil Trekker.

With an emphasis on traveling these vlogs are meant to encourage everyone to go out, explore & make the most out of every situation they come across.

🔥 This is a YouTube experience like no other, filled with adventure, adrenaline, and unexpected twists! Don't miss out – hit that SUBSCRIBE button, give this video a THUMBS UP, and join me on this unforgettable journey into the depths of Shappiere mining site!
🔔 Make sure to turn on your NOTIFICATIONS so you're the first to know when the next thrilling episode drops! Get ready to be on the edge of your seat as we explore the unknown together!

நான் புவனி தரன், பேக் பேக்கர், ஹிட்சிகர், வோல்கர் & ட்ரெக்கர், உலகம் முழுவதும் பயணம் செய்து எனது அனுபவங்களை அனைவருடனும் பகிர்ந்து கொள்கிறேன்.

புதிய இடங்களைப் பார்ப்பது, வெவ்வேறு கலாச்சாரத்தை அனுபவிப்பது, மக்களைப் பற்றி அறிந்து கொள்வது, இந்த அழகான உலகத்தை தமிழ் ட்ரெக்கர் வழியாக உங்களுக்குக் காட்ட முயற்சிப்பேன்.

எனது இந்த பயணத்தில் அனைவரையும் வெளியே செல்லவும், ஆராயவும், அவர்கள் சந்திக்கும் ஒவ்வொரு சூழ்நிலையையும் சிறப்பாகப் பயன்படுத்தவும் ஊக்குவிப்பதாகும்.

I'm Bhuvani Dharan, Solo travel enthusiast, Backpacker, hitchhiker, vlogger & trekker who travels the world and shares my experiences with everyone.

My videos consist of my spontaneous everyday life as each day is a new adventure.

Love to see new places, experience different culture, learn about people, taste different food and more. I will try to show you this beautiful world via Tamil Trekker.

With an emphasis on traveling these vlogs are meant to encourage everyone to go out, explore & make the most out of every situation they come across.

snippet.title: Bhagwan Bharose Trailer | Shiladitya Bora | Indian Ocean |Vinay Pathak |Masumeh Makhija | 13 October
snippet.description:
In a world blinded by faith, can innocence win over hate?
Presenting the official theatrical trailer of Bhagwan Bharose, a film by Shiladitya Bora. Releasing on October 13, 2023 in cinemas across India, North America, UK, Australia, and New Zealand.

India Release by PVR INOX Pictures
International Distribution by Rhythm Boyz Entertainment

Platoon One Films presents
in association with Lighthouse Innoventures, Sri Sathya Sai Arts
A Platoon One production

Ab Toh Sab Bhagwan Bharose 

Directed by Shiladitya Bora 
Music by Indian Ocean

Story: Sudhakar Nilmani (Eklavya)
Screenplay & Dialogues: Sudhakar Nilmani, Mohit Chauhan 
Lyrics: Sanjeev Sharma
Producers: Prasanna Vithanage, Shiladitya Bora, Milapsinh Jadeja, K.K.Radhamohan, Sanyukta Gupta, Shilpi Agarwal
Co-Producer: Ankur Indravijay Singh
Director of Photography: Surjodeep Ghosh
Editor: Sooraj Gunjal
Production Designer: Rishabh Kushwaha
Costume Designer: Shilpi Agarwal
Hair & Make-Up: Yogita Adhikari
Location Sound: Sabyasachi Pal
Sound Design & Mix: Adeep Singh Manki, Anindit Roy (C.A.S)
DI & VFX: Afterplay Studios (Maddy)
DI Colorist: Pranab Manna
VFX Supervisor: Ajay Gaikwad
Line Production: Pritam Chowdhury (Teamwork)
Casting: Shiladitya Bora, Mayank Bawa, Mahesh Sharma
Acting Coach: Kanishka Aggarwal (The Artist Collective)
Associate Producer: Raviraaj Paatel
Director’s Assistant: Pavithra Sreekumar
Assistant Producer: Nikita Naiknavare
Creative Marketing: Jahan Bakshi 
Platoon One Team: Meenakshi Laxminarayan, Kanisha Shah
Publicity Design: Seek Red
Promo Campaign: Promoshop
Publicist: Hema Upadhyay
